OL,3,C'No longer living, just existing'
OL,4,Cpensioner hit by e-bike still in
OL,5,Cconstant pain
OL,7,FWarning this article incudes
OL,8,Fdistessing images.
OL,10,FTwo men from Wigan have been sentenced
OL,11,Ffor their part in an e-bike crash that
OL,12,Fleft a pensioner with life-changing
OL,13,Finjuries.
OL,15,FOn 1 August 2023, Margaret Scaldwell
OL,16,Fwas crossing Orrell Road in Wigan when
OL,17,Fshe was hit by an e-bike being driven
OL,18,Fby Kian Monks at about 40 mph in a 30
OL,19,Fmph zone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
