OL,4,Cpensioner hit by e-bike still in
OL,5,Cconstant pain
OL,7,FCCTV shown to Bolton Crown Court
OL,8,Fshowed Mrs Scaldwell, 70 being knocked
OL,9,Foff her feet and thrown down the road
OL,10,Fafter the collision.
OL,12,FThe impact broke her spine, pelvis,
OL,13,Fboth arms, and 19 ribs and she needed
OL,14,Fsteel plates fitted in her face.
OL,16,FThe court also heard the emergency
OL,17,Fcalls made in the minutes after the
OL,18,Fcollision where nearby drivers
OL,19,Fdescribed the horrific collision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
