OL,7,FKian Monks, who used to play Wigan
OL,8,FAthletic's Youth team was 19 at the
OL,9,Ftime of the crash.
OL,11,FHe had previously admitted to causing
OL,12,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,13,FToday he was sentenced to 2 years and
OL,14,F3 months in prison.
OL,16,FJoel Pilling, who was 20 at the time
OL,17,Fof the collision had pleaded guilty to
OL,18,Fdangerous driving and aiding and
OL,19,Fabetting serious injury by dangerous
OL,20,Fdriving.
