OL,7,FIn her victim impact statement Mrs
OL,8,FScaldwell said she was an "independent
OL,9,Flady who always had a smile on my
OL,10,Fface" but is now "no longer living and
OL,11,Fis just existing".
OL,13,FAs a result of the collision she
OL,14,Frelies on medication for the constant
OL,15,Fpain and to sleep at night. She said
OL,16,Fshe has "nightmares and constant
OL,17,Fearache" after the collision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
