OL,3,C'No longer living, just existing'
OL,4,Cpensioner hit by e-bike still in
OL,5,Cconstant pain
OL,7,FOn the day of the crash Joel Pilling
OL,8,Fhad picked up Kian Monks on the bike,
OL,9,Fbut later they had swapped so Monks
OL,10,Fwas driving and Pilling was the
OL,11,Fpassenger. Monks insisted that he had
OL,12,Fno memory of swapping drivers, so he
OL,13,Fbelieved he was the passenger at the
OL,14,Ftime of the collision.
OL,16,FBoth Monks and Pilling fled the scene
OL,17,Fimmediately after the crash. Monks was
OL,18,Farrested at a nearby taxi rank and
OL,19,FPilling turned himself into Police
OL,20,Fseveral hours after the crash.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
