OL,4,Cpensioner hit by e-bike still in
OL,5,Cconstant pain
OL,7,FMonks told the court that "I woke up
OL,8,Fin a pool of my own blood, I thought I
OL,9,Fwas going to die and needed to get
OL,10,Fhome to my Mum and sister". He said he
OL,11,Fhad "no recollection" of hitting
OL,12,Fanyone.
OL,14,FMobile phone footage showed to the
OL,15,Fcourt saw him riding the bike away
OL,16,Ffrom the scene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
