OL,4,Cpensioner hit by e-bike still in
OL,5,Cconstant pain
OL,7,FKian Monks said he has written a
OL,8,Fletter of apology to Mrs Scaldwell and
OL,9,Fsaid "I feel horrendous about my
OL,10,Factions and never set out to hurt
OL,11,Fanyone" saying he is "sincerely sorry"
OL,13,FMonks played as a centre-forward for
OL,14,FWigan Athletic's Youth Team during
OL,15,F2020/21 season. He has been without a
OL,16,Fclub since July 2022.
OL,18,FHe was described in court as having a
OL,19,F"promising football career" that also
OL,20,Fincluded some time as an academy
OL,21,Fplayer at Bolton Wanderers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
