OL,7,FHe suffered a "career ending injury to
OL,8,Fhis ankle" and then started to get in
OL,9,Fwith the wrong crowd and make "stupid
OL,10,Fdecision" when his future in football
OL,11,Fcame to an end.
OL,13,FThe court was told by Joel Pilling's
OL,14,Fdefence team that the now 22 year old
OL,15,Fis a reformed character who was in
OL,16,Fwith the 'wrong crowd' at the time of
OL,17,Fthe collision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
