OL,7,FHe has shown genuine remorse for his
OL,8,Fbehaviour and has good prospects for
OL,9,Frehabilitation as he is working
OL,10,Ftowards an apprenticeship and a career
OL,11,Fas a tradesman.
OL,13,FJoel Pilling, who was 20 at the time
OL,14,Fof the collision had pleaded guilty to
OL,15,Fdangerous driving and aiding and
OL,16,Fabetting serious injury by dangerous
OL,17,Fdriving.
